.TH minss 1 "April 1993" "Scilab Group" "Scilab Function"
.so man1/sci.an 
.SH NAME
minss - minimal realization
.SH CALLING SEQUENCE
.nf
[slc]=minss( sl [,tol])
.fi
.SH PARAMETERS
.TP 10
sl,slc      
: \fVsyslin\fR lists (linear systems in state-space form)
.TP
tol
: real (threshold for rank determination (see \fVcontr\fR))
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fVminss\fR returns in \fVslc\fR the minimal realization of \fVsl\fR.
.SH EXAMPLE
.nf
sl=syslin('c',[1 0;0 2],[1;0],[2 1]);
ssprint(sl);
ssprint(minss(sl))
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO 
contr, minreal, arhnk, contrss, obsvss

